862cfd06f46b23208e05e282a93b0f6fc2c714db.text_content: Aegis is a free, secure and open source 2FA app

d3a29f3bc2137bd52546db34f7cc92faf8310d18.text_content:
Aegis is a security-focused 2FA app. Tokens are stored in a vault, that can optionally be encrypted with a password of your choosing. If an attacker obtains your encrypted vault file, they will not be able to access the contents without knowing the password.

We've preselected the option that we think would fit best for your device.
No password is needed to unlock the vault and it will not be encrypted. This option is not recommended.
A password is needed to unlock the vault.
In addition to a password, biometrics registered on this device, like a fingerprint or your face, can be used to unlock the vault.
